title: The Winds of Winter: Alayne I (2015)
description:
Ashaya & Aziz devour this chapter as if it were a 12 foot tall lemon cake threatened by a pimply gingerlad. The original companion to our Valar Rereadis version with a different approach and focus, published May 27, 2015.
